This recipe has possibilities but we found it needs a stronger flavor. Next time we'll reduce the amount of water and increase the spices.

Rating: 4
Delicious and easy sweet-and-savoury dish. The only mistake I made was using too much orange peel (which I used instead of the tangerine) resulting in a slightly bitter taste. Otherwise very tasty. I served it with cauliflower with ginger and mustard seeds from Gourmet, a nice combination.

Rating: 2
We found this dish to be rather disappointing and bland. If I make it again I would cut the pork into much smaller pieces and would add hot oil to jazz it up a bit.

