we enjoyed this dish. very different. BUT it was time-consuming! i've never made pork butt before and wow... is it fatty!!! it took me an hour to trim it(ok, maybe i'm a little obsessive). after that, it wasn't too hard. maybe i'll try it again with a less fatty cut of pork.